data.description: Confirmed appointment showings only.  Well maintained home.  Modern kitchen with granite, interior laundry room, split floor plan, den, exterior shed. NO HOA, No pet restrictions, large yard, driveway large enough for cars and small boat.  Bathroom recently remodeled. Hurricane Impact windows installed in the main house area not the den in 2019. Gutters installed in 2022.  Sprinkler system on well water.  Home is being sold AS-IS.  Fire pit in back yard does not go with sale. Standalone Freezer does not go with the sale.  All measurements are deemed reliable not accurate.
